{
  "stem": "14168.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was an old man there who handed me my passport, and he said, you are one of the lucky ones.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I shuddered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, what are you talking about?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, I wear the Nazi badge, but I'm one of Jehovah's witnesses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, you will survive, and we won't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you had people like that once in a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some people had guts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I got the-- the visa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I bought a steamship ticket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That steamship ticket also had to be paid for in dollars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a friend from my earliest school years who had emigrated to Holland, to [INAUDIBLE], Eindhoven, as an engineer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he got the Dutch Jewish Committee to help me finance my steamship ticket.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was about-- Then I left Germany on the 20th of December, 1938.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still remember standing there on the platform of the railroad station, saying goodbye to my family-- my mother and my fiance, about whom I want to talk in a little while.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took me to the-- and the Gestapo had previously-- or the customs opened my suitcase, to make sure that I wasn't gonna take anything more than the clothes on my back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I still see them disappear as the train rolled on to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I arrived in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had-- this friend in Holland had asked me-- since the boat that I was going to take would stop in Antwerp on its way from Hamburg, he said, why don't you come to-- to Holland, spend a few days with me, then I'll take you to the boat in Antwerp?",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was about an hour away from there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- I decided to do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I was--",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
